steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jit015h" and Comment "[INDEX-DATE]"
Then I should see the table with Name "jit015h" display
When I add new column with Name "indexdate" Type "date" for Table name "jit015h"
When I open popup to see column infos Name "indexdate" of table with Name "jit015h"
When I check checkbox popup Name "Indexed"
When I press Save button modal popup
When I open add-index popup of table "jit015h"
Then I should see dropdown Index column index "1" of Index number "1" has value "indexdate"
